
### Simple project testing different ways of styling react app  
![Design preview for the CSimple Cards  coding challenge in max react course](./src/assets/project-preview.png)


## lessons

1-conditional or dynamic way.
2-styled components.
//style components, definitely a nice package for, well, styling components and ensuring that components really only affect the styles on which you set them up.
3-CSS modules.
// CSS Modules is a feature which is only available in projects that are configured to support it because it needs a code transformation that needs to be done before your code runs in the browser.
